           <div class="item column-1">
    <article class="art-post"><div class="art-postmetadataheader"><h2 class="art-postheader"><a href="/news/43-magnificent.html">MAGNIFICENT</a></h2></div><div class="art-postcontent clearfix"><div class="art-article"><p>
	<img alt="" src="/images/logo_BBI_RIA.png" style="width: 160px; height: 90px;" /><strong>MAGNIFICENT </strong></p>
<p>
	Reliable microalgae products serving market demands for a sustainable future</p>
<p>
	<strong>MAGNIFICENT</strong> - <strong>M</strong>icroalgae <strong>A</strong>s a <strong>G</strong>reen source for <strong>N</strong>utritional <strong>I</strong>ngredients for <strong>F</strong>ood/Feed and <strong>I</strong>ngredients for <strong>C</strong>osmetics by cost-<strong>E</strong>ffective <strong>N</strong>ew <strong>T</strong>echnologies, is a 4-year project funded by BBI-RIA (Bio-based Industries Research and Innovation Action) with an EU contribution of EUR 5.330.572,50.</p>
<p>
	&nbsp;</p>
</div><p class="readmore"><a class="readon art-button" href="/news/43-magnificent.html">Read&#160;more:&#160;MAGNIFICENT</a></p></div></article>    </div>
                    <span class="row-separator"></span>
</div>
                            <div class="items-row cols-1 row-1">
           <div class="item column-1">
    <article class="art-post"><div class="art-postmetadataheader"><h2 class="art-postheader"><a href="/news/29-naturextracts-and-madebiotech-awarded-at-the-25th-edition-of-the-top-100-best-and-biggest-companies-of-madeira.html">NatureXtracts and MadeBiotech awarded at the 25th edition of the Top 100 Best and Biggest Companies of Madeira</a></h2></div><div class="art-postcontent clearfix"><div class="art-article"><p>
	&nbsp;</p>
<table border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1">
	<tbody>
		<tr>
			<td style="width: 426px;">
				<img alt="" class="cke-resize" src="/images/00_Custom_4.jpg" style="width: 400px; font-family: Arial; font-size: medium;" /></td>
			<td style="width: 436px;">
				<p>
					&nbsp;</p>
				<p>
					The 25th edition of the&nbsp;<strong>Top 100 Best and Biggest Companies</strong>&nbsp;<strong>of Madeira </strong>took place at the Congress Centre of Madeira in the last November 12th.</p>
				<p>
					This event aims to reward companies from various industry sectors that performed best results in 2013.</p>
				<p>
					The guest of honor of this edition was the Prime Minister of Portugal, Pedro Passos Coelho.&nbsp;</p>
			</td>
		</tr>
	</tbody>
</table>
</div><p class="readmore"><a class="readon art-button" href="/news/29-naturextracts-and-madebiotech-awarded-at-the-25th-edition-of-the-top-100-best-and-biggest-companies-of-madeira.html">Read&#160;more:&#160;NatureXtracts&#160;and&#160;MadeBiotech&#160;awarded&#160;at&#160;the&#160;25th&#160;edition&#160;of&#160;the&#160;Top&#160;100&#160;Best&#160;and&#160;Biggest...</a></p></div></article>    </div>
